event Delegated(address indexed asset, address indexed delegatee, bool success)
event OwnershipTransferStarted(address indexed previousOwner, address indexed newOwner)
event OwnershipTransferred(address indexed previousOwner, address indexed newOwner)
event RewardDistributed(address indexed token, uint256 amount)
event RewardHarvested(address indexed staker, address indexed token, uint128 amountToken)
event RewardHarvestedFromUnlock(address indexed staker, address indexed token, bool isOldBaseAsset, uint256[] ids, uint128 amountToken)
event RewardTokenAdded(address token, uint256 index, uint128 precisionDelta)
event TizzClaimed(address indexed staker, uint256[] ids, uint128 amountTizz)
event TizzStaked(address indexed staker, uint128 amountTizz)
event TizzUnstaked(address indexed staker, uint128 amountTizz)
event UnlockManagerUpdated(address indexed manager, bool authorized)
event UnlockScheduleRevoked(address indexed staker, uint256 indexed index)

event UnlockScheduled(address indexed staker, uint256 indexed index, tuple(uint128 totalTizz, uint128 claimedTizz, uint128 debtBaseAsset, uint48 start, uint48 duration, bool revocable, uint8 unlockType, uint16 __placeholder) schedule)
function createUnlockSchedule(tuple(uint128 totalTizz, uint48 start, uint48 duration, bool revocable, uint8 unlockType) _schedule, address _staker)

function getUnlockSchedules(address _staker, uint256 _index) view returns (tuple(uint128 totalTizz, uint128 claimedTizz, uint128 debtBaseAsset, uint48 start, uint48 duration, bool revocable, uint8 unlockType, uint16 __placeholder))

function getUnlockSchedules(address _staker) view returns (tuple(uint128 totalTizz, uint128 claimedTizz, uint128 debtBaseAsset, uint48 start, uint48 duration, bool revocable, uint8 unlockType, uint16 __placeholder)[])
function pendingRewardBaseAssetFromUnlocks(address _staker, uint256[] _ids) view returns (uint128 pending)
function pendingRewardTokensFromUnlocks(address _staker, uint256[] _ids) view returns (uint128[] pendingTokens)

function releasableTizz(tuple(uint128 totalTizz, uint128 claimedTizz, uint128 debtBaseAsset, uint48 start, uint48 duration, bool revocable, uint8 unlockType, uint16 __placeholder) _schedule, uint48 _timestamp) pure returns (uint128)
function rewardTokenState(address) view returns (uint128 accRewardPerTizz, uint128 precisionDelta)
function stakers(address) view returns (uint128 stakedTizz, uint128 debtBaseAsset)

function unlockedTizz(tuple(uint128 totalTizz, uint128 claimedTizz, uint128 debtBaseAsset, uint48 start, uint48 duration, bool revocable, uint8 unlockType, uint16 __placeholder) _schedule, uint48 _timestamp) pure returns (uint128)
function userTokenRewards(address, address) view returns (uint128 debtToken, uint128 __placeholder)
function userTokenUnlockRewards(address, address, uint256) view returns (uint128 debtToken, uint128 __placeholder)
